= Dr. Adam Leeper

I am an amateur recording engineer and live-sound guy.
This page contains music recorded by me over the years. Enjoy!

== Soul Practitioners
This is my active cover band from 2024-present. Pop, rock, and more from the last 7 decades.
- [^https://www.youtube.com/@SoulPractitionersOfficial YouTube Channel]
- [^https://soundcloud.com/soul-practitioners/albums Soundcloud Profile]

